title: Run into a warning with vxm.layers.SpatialTransformer
body:
**Task** (what are you trying to do/register?)

3D CT registration 

**What have you tried**

using voxelmorph library functions to transform moving image with a deformation field. 

**Details of experiments**

Environment: 
tensorflow                2.0.0  
voxelmorph                0.1

I ran into this warning when I trained my model. I am not sure what it exactly means. Model can be trained, but I am worried if my moving image is not really transformed by a dense field, instead it is transformed by identity mapping. Should I worry about this? Have you met similar problem? Thanks!
